E-MailRelay windows build
=========================

cmake
-----
Cmake 2.8.12.1 source code:

	https://cmake.org/files/v2.8/cmake-2.8.12.1.tar.gz
	https://cmake.org/files/v2.8/cmake-2.8.12.1.zip

Build on windows using "nmake":

	cd cmake
	mkdir build
	cd build
	nmake cmake
	PATH=<cwd>;%PATH%

Build on windows without "nmake":

	cd cmake
	mkdir build
	cd build
	..\..\makecmake.bat
	PATH=<cwd>;%PATH%

perl
----
Perl 5.38.0 source code:

	https://www.cpan.org/src/5.0/perl-5.38.0.tar.gz

Build on windows using "nmake":

	cd perl
	cd win32
	vi Makefile [set CCTYPE]
	nmake 
	cd ..
	PATH=<cwd>;%PATH%

Build on windows without "nmake":

	...

qt5
---
Qt source code:

	git clone git://code.qt.io/qt/qt5.git qt5
	cd qt5
	git checkout 5.12
	perl init-repository --module-subset=qtbase

Build on windows using "perl" and "nmake":

	perl emailrelay/libexec/qtbuild.pl

Clean with:

	rmdir /s /q qt-build-x64

emailrelay
----------
E-MailRelay source.

Build on windows using "perl" and "cmake":

	cd emailrelay
	perl winbuild.pl

